    "They also felt that the system should provide more user control and that the ignored recommendations and explanations should not reappear in the future.",
    "Holistically, an explainable system would impact their overall trust in the system.",
    "One of the participants said, I will be able to find similar content with more ease if I understand how the recommendation works a little bit.",
